    public abstract class AbstractCEPBasePatternOperator<IN,OUT>
extends org.apache.flink.streaming.api.operators.AbstractStreamOperator<OUT>
implements org.apache.flink.streaming.api.operators.OneInputStreamOperator<IN,OUT>
    Base class for CEP pattern operator. The operator uses a NFA to detect complex event patterns. The detected event patterns are then outputted to the down stream operators.

        protected abstract void processEvent(NFA<IN> nfa,
                                     IN event,

        Process the given event by giving it to the NFA and outputting the produced set of matched event sequences.
        参数:
        nfa - NFA to be used for the event detection
        event - The current event to be processed
        timestamp - The timestamp of the event
